              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3kk94z6n/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>incurring any expenses send the along &amp; if you have any<lb/> Jewish calendars you\n                will send me a few doz.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr I Newman</persName> &amp; <persName>P. Myers</persName>\n                have recd the <sic>occident</sic> since<lb/> I wrote to you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><sic>I</sic> conclusion, I remark that you owe me no thanks &amp;\n                are under<lb/> no obligation to me whatever <del>?</del> for the little trouble<lb/>\n                I have if any in gaining for you subscribers for the <sic>occident</sic><lb/> or in\n                effecting some sales for your religious books. I am free<lb/> to confess, that,\n                although I shall always feel happy to confer<lb/> a favour or serve in any manner my\n                fellow Neighbour particular<lb/> a fellow believer, yet my prime object is in the\n                above, to arouse<lb/> the <add>יהודים</add>\n                <add>?</add> from that fatal indifference about their Religion<lb/> in which they\n                are alas, so fearfully sunk &amp; this is the main<lb/> cause why I am so desirous\n                of spreading among them some<lb/> good &amp; religious works like the\n                    <sic>occident</sic>; but if in doing<lb/> so, I can or do serve you in any way I\n                shall feel most happy<lb/> but as above stated the prime object is <del>in doing\n                    so</del> a desire<lb/> of doing some good in <placeName>Israel</placeName>, or\n                if I <sic>incidently</sic> serve you it<lb/> is not the primary object consequently\n                you owe me nothing.<lb/> I desire no thanks &amp; neither Reward.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">I am my dear sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Yours very truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">B M Emanuel</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>P. S. If I can serve you</p>\n            <p>in any thing or transaction which</p>\n            <p>you may have here in the <placeName>south</placeName></p>\n            <p>you are always welcome to write to me</p>\n            <p>about it, I shall cheerfully attend to any thing</p>\n            <p>you may require</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3kk94z6n/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
